{"title_page": "Armorial of Portuguese colonies", "text_new": "{{expand language|topic=|langcode=pt|otherarticle=Anexo:Bras\u00f5es de antigos territ\u00f3rios portugueses|date=October 2012}}\nThe [[coats of arms]] of the [[Portuguese Empire]]'s [[colonies]] were all of a uniform style following 1935.{{refn|published in the Di\u00e1rio do Gov\u00earno<ref>{{Citation |url=https://dre.pt/web/guest/pesquisa/-/search/577167/details/maximized |title=Portaria 8098: Aprova as ordena\u00e7\u00f5es das armas das col\u00f3nias que, nos termos da Constitu\u00ef\u00e7\u00e3o e do Acto Colonial, formam o Imp\u00e9rio Colonial Portugu\u00eas |work=Di\u00e1rio do Gov\u00earno n.\u00ba 104/1935, S\u00e9rie I de 1935-05-08, 597-599 |language=pt }}</ref>}} Two of them had, however, been using provisional coats of arms of the same style shortly prior to this.\n\n==Gallery==\nThis gallery include the lesser coats of arms. The years given are for the coats of arms.\n\n<gallery>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese West Africa.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Angola]]<br/>(1935-1975)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Cape Verde.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Cape Verde]]<br/>(1935-1975)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Guinea.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Guinea]]<br/>(1935-1974)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese India.svg|<center>[[Portuguese India]]<br/>(1935-1961)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Macau.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Macau]]<br/>(1935-1999)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese East Africa.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Mozambique]]<br/>(1935-1975)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Sao Tome and Principe.svg|<center>[[Portuguese S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe]]<br/>(1935-1975)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Timor.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Timor]]<br/>(1935-1975/2002)</center>\n</gallery>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Coat of arms of Portugal]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Colonial coats of arms}}\n{{Portuguese overseas empire}}\n\n[[Category:Former Portuguese colonies]]\n[[Category:Portuguese coats of arms]]\n[[Category:Armorials by country subdivision|Portugal]]\n", "text_old": "{{expand language|topic=|langcode=pt|otherarticle=Anexo:Bras\u00f5es de antigos territ\u00f3rios portugueses|date=October 2012}}\nThe [[coats of arms]] of the [[Portuguese Empire]]'s [[colonies]] were all of a uniform style following 1935.{{refn|published in the Di\u00e1rio do Gov\u00earno<ref>{{Citation |url=https://dre.pt/web/guest/pesquisa/-/search/577167/details/maximized |title=Portaria 8098: Aprova as ordena\u00e7\u00f5es das armas das col\u00f3nias que, nos termos da Constitu\u00ef\u00e7\u00e3o e do Acto Colonial, formam o Imp\u00e9rio Colonial Portugu\u00eas |work=Di\u00e1rio do Gov\u00earno n.\u00ba 104/1935, S\u00e9rie I de 1935-05-08, 597-599 |language=pt }}</ref>}} Two of them had, however, been using provisional coats of arms of the same style shortly prior to this.\n\n==Gallery==\nThis gallery include the lesser coats of arms. The years given are for the coats of arms.\n\n<gallery>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese West Africa.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Angola]]<br/>(1935-1975)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Cape Verde.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Cape Verde]]<br/>(1935-1975)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Guinea.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Guinea]]<br/>(1935-1974)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese India.svg|<center>[[Portuguese India]]<br/>(1935-1961)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Macau.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Macau]]<br/>(1935-1999)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese East Africa.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Mozambique]]<br/>(1935-1975)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Sao Tome and Principe.svg|<center>[[Portuguese S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe]]<br/>(1935-1975)</center>\nFile:Lesser coat of arms of Portuguese Timor.svg|<center>[[Portuguese Timor]]<br/>(1935-1975/2002)</center>\n</gallery>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Coat of arms of Portugal]]\n\n{{Colonial coats of arms}}\n{{Portuguese overseas empire}}\n\n[[Category:Former Portuguese colonies]]\n[[Category:Portuguese coats of arms]]\n[[Category:Armorials by country subdivision|Portugal]]\n", "name_user": "G\u00fcnniX", "label": "safe", "comment": "Reflist", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armorial_of_Portuguese_colonies"}
