ory:Lists of Indian television series|Colors]]\n[[Category:Lists of television series by network|Colors]]\n[[Category:Viacom 18]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}} \n{{Use Indian English|date=September 2015}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2015}}\n\nThe following is the list of current and former broadcasts by the Indian television channel [[Colors TV]].\n\n==Current broadcasts==\n===Drama===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Show\n!Ref. \n|-\n|2020\u2013\n|''[[Barrister Babu]]''\n|\n|-\n|2019\u2013\n|''[[Choti Sarrdaarni]]''\n|\n|-\n|2019\u2013\n|''[[Naagin (2015 TV series)|Naagin : Bhagya Ka Jahreela Khel]]''\n|\n|-\n|2020\u2013\n|''[[Naati Pinky Ki Lambi Love Story]]''\n|\n|-\n|2016\u2013\n|''[[Shakti - Astitva Ke Ehsaas Ki]]''\n|\n|-\n|2019\u2013\n|''[[Shrimad Bhagwat Mahapuran]]''\n|\n|-\n|2019\u2013\n|''[[Shubharambh]]''\n|\n|-\n|2019\u2013\n|''[[Vidya (TV series)|Vidya]]'' \n|\n|}\n\n===Reality===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Show\n! Ref. \n|-\n|2020\u2013\n| ''[[Fear Factor: Khatron Ke Khiladi 10]]''\n|<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/television/reality-tv/story/khatron-ke-khiladi-10-shivin-narang-and-smiriti-kalra-have-a-blast-in-bulgaria-1593834-2019-08-31 |title=Khatron Ke Khiladi 10: Shivin Narang and Smiriti Kalra have a blast in Bulgaria |last=DelhiAugust 31 |first=Indo-Asian News Service New |last2=August 31 |first2=2019UPDATED: |website=India Today |publisher=[[India Today]] |location=India |access-date=2020-01-20 |last3=Ist |first3=2019 13:56}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Upcoming broadcasts==\n* ''[[Ishq Mein Marjawan 2]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pinkvilla.com/tv/news-gossip/ishq-mein-marjawan-2-promo-helly-shah-and-vishal-vashishtha-weave-story-love-revenge-and-sacrifice-502484|title=Ishq Mein Marjawan 2 PROMO: Helly Shah and Vishal Vashishtha weave a story of love, revenge and sacrifice|website=PINKVILLA|language=en|access-date=20